Nigeria’s hit musician, Runtown has dropped the visuals for his latest single Oh Oh Oh. The triple Oh song takes a step away from the Mad Over You crooner’s signature Oh Oh Oh is a follow up to his single “Unleash”. Read More: Watch: “Dabebi” By Mr Eazi Featuring King Promise & Maleek Berry The song was produced by Del B. Enjoy!  Runtown has recently found himself in a tussle with his former record label, Eric Many Entertainment. Only yesterday the 20th of December, the manager of Eric Many, Johnson Adumike, reportedly wrote via social media that he has been banned from entering the US because his brother who secured the US visa using Eric Many has since refused to come back despite the expiration of the visa.